        Open K-Electric Bill Checker &rarr;
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-neutral-200 pt-6">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        <a href="/k-electric-bill/" class="text-sm bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-primary-700 font-semibold hover:underline">K-Electric Bill Checker &rarr;</a>
        <a href="/blog/how-to-check-k-electric-bill/" class="text-sm bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-neutral-600 hover:underline">How to Check K-Electric Bill &rarr;</a>
        <a href="/blog/how-to-pay-online/" class="text-sm bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-neutral-600 hover:underline">Online Payment Guide &rarr;</a>
        <a href="/blog/" class="text-sm bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-neutral-600 hover:underline">More Guides &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
